    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Rupavahinik Corporation is in the hands of the protesters",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Protesters against the government today (13) surrounded the Sri Lanka Television Corporation and staged a demonstration.",
        "After this, the protestors who entered the Sri Lanka Television Corporation interrupted the broadcast and conveyed the objective of their protest live.",
        "It is noteworthy that the live broadcast of the Sri Lanka Broadcasting Corporation has been suspended until now."
      ],
